2020.05.24 Two distinct approaches for distrib files
	* report: template files for report, accessed by hand with
	os.path.join( os.path.dirname(os.path.abspath(__file__)), "../report")
	* peroba/data: reference files used by backbone (minimap2, snps from `lineages`), one of
	str(pkg_resources.resource_filename( __name__, 'data/singletons.csv'))
	os.path.join(str(pkg_resources.resource_filename( __name__, 'data/')), "singletons.csv")

